"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1929749-Olympic-surfer-rescued\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Australian surfing sensation Jack Robinson has opened up about a near-drowning experience during the Paris Olympics, held in Tahiti.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9903419902058965, \"rank\": 0.009656199570860188, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 31, \"end\": 35, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"score\": 0.8769133808855517, \"rank\": 0.12724896249618703, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\"}, {\"begin\": 36, \"end\": 44, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.9890324936114584, \"rank\": 0.010004145465080005, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}, {\"begin\": 127, \"end\": 133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.999917359802303, \"rank\": 8.22451920930229e-05, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 26-year-old, who is among the world's top surfers, had a stellar performance that saw him defeat world No 1 John Florence amid treacherous conditions in French Polynesia.\", \"from\": 135, \"to\": 309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 245, \"end\": 251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/First_Epistle_of_John\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"1 John\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/First_Epistle_of_John\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/First_Epistle_of_John\"}, {\"begin\": 252, \"end\": 260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florence\", \"score\": 0.9915670522503957, \"rank\": 0.008504667163445681, \"text\": \"Florence\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florence\"}, {\"begin\": 299, \"end\": 308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9892404984230054, \"rank\": 0.01087652684372792, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A storm system led to massive waves and resulted in the postponement of the women's round three heat due to safety concerns.\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 435, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Robinson recounted his terrifying ordeal after several wipe-outs necessitated rescue by jet-ski.\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 436, \"end\": 444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.9890324936114584, \"rank\": 0.010004145465080005, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I got dragged over the bottom and almost had a two wave hold under,\\\" he confessed.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 617, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not get much air.\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 642, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There wasn't much time.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I got reminded of so many guys who have had so many bad wipe-outs here.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have had some pretty bad (wipe-outs) but in a contest it's different.\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 812, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You have way more adrenaline and there is way more on the line.\\\"\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 877, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He added that while he's experienced severe wipe-outs before, competing adds an extra layer of intensity due to the adrenaline and high stakes involved.\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 1031, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the scare, Robinson triumphed with a score of 13.94, outdoing Florence's 9.07.\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1052, \"end\": 1060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.9890324936114584, \"rank\": 0.010004145465080005, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, he emphasised the inherent dangers of the ocean, likening the power of a wave to an avalanche.\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Every other sport is in a court or a stadium,\\\" he pointed out.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are in an ocean.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1311, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is the biggest, most powerful source of life we have on this planet.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1383, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"'The waves are so powerful.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1413, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It does not relate to any other sport.\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe an avalanche coming down on your head on a mountain.\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe it's similar to that.\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's so dangerous and so crazy.\\\"\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1572, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Robinson will face fellow Australian Ethan Ewing in the quarter-finals - with the latter suffering his own string of wipe-outs in the huge waves after defeating Connor O'Leary.\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1574, \"end\": 1582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"score\": 0.9890324936114584, \"rank\": 0.010004145465080005, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harold_E._Robinson\"}, {\"begin\": 1600, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9903419902058965, \"rank\": 0.009656199570860188, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1735, \"end\": 1741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connor_MacLeod\", \"score\": 0.7677338767041868, \"rank\": 0.3025346794749419, \"text\": \"Connor\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connor_MacLeod\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connor_MacLeod\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1861, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1938, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1971, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"I had some wipeouts but stoked it paid off,\\\" Ewing said.\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have so much water in my head right now.\",